{
  "stem": "20848.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there-- I remembers the SS in-- in-- in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was somebody called Hessler who you-- we used to call him [GERMAN], the liar.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he was approachable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could approach him and ask for something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he'll promise you that he's going to give it to you or do it for you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he never did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to call him liar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day when I was still in Birkenau-- I have to tell you that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told you it won't be chronicle-- chronicle order.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I have to tell you-- I feel I have to tell you that one day when I was still in Birkenau, the transport from Lodz started coming.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my auntie, my mother's sister, came with her two daughters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Her son and her husband must have been separated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a woman came with regards from my auntie to say that she's very hungry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was already from-- in a different lager, but also in-- in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and she's very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So immediately, you know, because I worked the [GERMAN], we sent through the woman two jumpers-- or three jumpers for the-- and bread for-- for my cousins, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she received it because we got a letter from her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The woman came again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, your auntie with your cousin has been put to gas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your other cousin's all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she-- and I was walking in the camp and I saw the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think her name was Mendel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went over to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You were not allowed to speak directly to any SS personnel, because you were rubbish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I went to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said to her, look-- in German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By that time, I could speak German.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
